Description: Fragments from a New Kingdom Book of the Dead naming a man Nebtawy (spelled Nebettawy) and a woman (his wife ?) Nuby alternately in the text.
Curator's comments: Another section of this papyrus is in University College London (UC71005)
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (133585) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/133585)
Condition: broken with one large and nine smaller fragments
